rsonal%20and%20professional%20life%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20However%2C%20he%20chose%20the%20perfect%20moment%20to%20put%20those%20difficulties%20behind%20him%20by%20delivering%20a%20match-winning%20performance%20for%20India%2C%20which%20secured%20the%20team%20its%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title.%20As%20the%20vice-captain%2C%20Pandya%20showcased%20his%20best%20bowling%20form%20in%20the%20final%20against%20South%20Africa%20on%20Saturday%20in%20Barbados%2C%20claiming%203%20wickets%20for%20just%2020%20runs.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20SPORTS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Ficc-mens-t20-world-cup%2Fhardik-pandya-just-a-boy-from-baroda-living-his-dream%2Farticleshow%2F111375383.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BHaven't%20Spoken%20A%20Word%26quot%3B%3A%20Crying%20Hardik%20Calls%20Out%20His%20Unfair%20Treatment%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EEmotional%20India's%20star%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20who%20was%20in%20tears%20after%20Men%20in%20Blue%20sealed%20T20%20World%20Cup%20glory%2C%20opened%20up%20on%20the%20challenging%20six%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20marquee%20event%20and%20said%20that%20he%20had%20kept%20quiet%20not%20speaking%20a%20word.%20Speaking%20to%20the%20broadcaster%20after%20the%20game%2C%20Pandya%20reflected%20on%20the%20previous%20six%20months%20and%20revealed%20that%20he%20had%20not%20lost%20his%20temper%20once%20when%20things%20were%20going%20wrong%2C%20which%20was%20precisely%20why%20the%20victory%20felt%20all%20the%20more%20meaningful.%20Mumbai%20Indians%20(MI)%20supporters%20and%20social%20media%20trolls%20had%20been%20very%20harsh%20to%20Pandya%20during%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMI%20brought%20back%20Pandya%20after%20a%20two-year%20stint%20with%20Gujarat%20Titans%20(GT)%2C%20which%20involved%20winning%20the%20title%20in%20t