-1236046592%2Famp%2F%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2024%2Fmusic%2Fglobal%2Fcoldplay-debuts-new-song-little-simz-glastonbury-1236046592%2Famp%2F%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22After%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20India%20Captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20Retires%20From%20T20Is%20Post%20Historic%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20Win%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3ETwo%20of%20India's%20greatest%20ever%20cricketers%20-%20Virat%20Kohli%20and%20Rohit%20Sharma%20-%20announced%20their%20T20I%20retirements%20on%20Saturday%2C%20after%20the%20side's%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20win.%20While%20Kohli%20announced%20his%20retirement%20minutes%20after%20the%20historic%20triumph%2C%20India%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20announced%20it%20in%20the%20official%20post%20match%20press%20conference.%C2%A0%20Rohit%2C%20who%20played%20a%20crucial%20role%20in%20India's%20triumphant%20campaign%2C%20confirmed%20that%20he%20would%20continue%20to%20represent%20India%20in%20ODIs%20and%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERohit%2C%20whose%20searing%2041-ball%2092-run%20knock%20in%20the%20Super%208s%20clash%20against%20Australia%20would%20be%20remembered%20for%20years%20to%20come%2C%20said%20he%20was%20'desperate'%20for%20the%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20was%20my%20last%20game%20as%20well.%20No%20better%20time%20to%20say%20goodbye.%20I%20wanted%20this%20(trophy)%20badly.%20It's%20very%20hard%20to%20put%20in%20words%2C%26quot%3B%20Rohit%20told%20the%20post-match%20press%20conference%20after%20ending%20India's%20over-a-decade%20long%20title%20drought.%20%26quot%3BThis%20what%20I%20wanted%20and%20it%20happened.%20I%20was%20very%20desperate%20for%20this%20in%20my%20life.%20Happy%20that%20we%20crossed%20the%20line%20this%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20announcement%20came%20on%20the%20heels%20of%20India's%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%2C%20a%20victory%20that%20brought%20immense%20joy%20and%20pride%20to%20the%20nation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20retirement%20marks%20the%20end%20of%20an%20illustrious%20T20I%20career%20during%20which%20he%20became%20the%20format's%20highest%20scorer%2C%20amassing%204231%20runs%20in%20159%20matches.%20He%20also%20holds%20the%20record%20for%20the%20most%20centuries%20in%20T20%20internationals%2C%20with%20five%20to%20his%20name.%20His%20T20I%20journey%20began%20with%20the%20inaugural%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%202007%2C%20where%20he%20was%20a%20key%20player%20in%20India's%20first%20title%20win.%20Now%2C%20as%20captain%2C%20he%20has%20led%20India%20to%20their%20second%20title%2C%20further%20cementing%20his%20legacy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20final%20match%20against%20South%20Africa%20was%20a%20nail-biter%2C%20with%20India%20defending%20a%20target%20of%20176%20runs.%20The%20Proteas%2C%20needing%2030%20runs%20from%20the%20last%2030%20deliveries%2C%20appeared%20to%20have%20the%20upper%20hand.%20However%2C%20India's%20bowlers%2C%20led%20by%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%2C%20and%20Arshdeep%20Singh%2C%20held%20their%20nerve%20in%20the%20crucial%20moments.%20Pandya%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20shone%20in%20the%20final%20over%2C%20successfully%20defending%2016%20runs%20and%20sealing%20a%20dramatic%20seven-run%20victory%20for%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20triumph%20was%20particularly%20special%20for%20Rohit%2C%20who%20had%20experienced%20both%20highs%20and%20lows%20in%20his%20cricketing%20career.%20The%20win%20was%20a%20testament%20to%20his%20leadership%2C%20resilience%2C%20and%20unwavering%20determination.%20Reflecting%20on%20his%20journey%2C%20Sharma%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI've%20loved%20every%20moment%20of%20this.%20I%20started%20my%20India%20career%20playing%20this%20format.%20This%20is%20what%20I%20wanted%2C%20I%20wanted%20to%20win%20the%20cup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20retirement%20follows%20that%20of%20his%20long-time%20teammate%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%2C%20who%20also%20announced%20his%20departure%20from%20T20%20internationals%20after%20the%20World%20Cup.%20Together%2C%20Sharma%20and%20Ko