nt%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fabhijeet-bhattacharya-reveals-shah-rukh-khan-was-hesitant-to-sing-i-am-the-best-from-phir-bhi-dil-hai-hindustani%2Farticleshow%2F111370040.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F111370040.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EShah%20Rukh%20Khan's%20versatility%20shines%20as%20he%20surprises%20with%20his%20singing%20skills%20in%20'I%20Am%20The%20Best.'%20Abhijeet%20Bhattacharya%20recalls%20the%20memorable%20recording%20session%20and%20the%20hit%20compositions%20they%20created%20together.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20India%20Defeated%20South%20Africa%20In%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Final%20-%205%20Turning%20Points%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20ended%20their%2011-year%20wait%20for%20an%20ICC%20trophy%20after%20they%20defeated%20South%20Africa%20by%20seven%20runs%20in%20a%20thrilling%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20final%20at%20the%20Kensington%20Oval%20in%20Bridgetown%2C%20Barbados%20on%20June%2029%2C%202024.%20India%20and%20South%20Africa%20named%20an%20unchanged%20playing%20XI%20after%20captain%20Rohit%20Sharma%20won%20the%20toss%20and%20opted%20to%20bat%20first.%20India%20got%20off%20to%20a%20flying%20start%20as%20openers%20Rohit%20and%20Virat%20Kohli%20added%2023%20runs%20before%20Keshav%20Maharaj%20removed%20the%20Indian%20captain%20(9)%20in%20the%20second%20over.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Men%20in%20Blue%20then%20suffered%20massive%20blows%20as%20Rishabh%20Pant%20(0)%20and%20Suryakumar%20Yadav%20(3)%20departed%20in%20quick%20succession.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKohli%20(76)%20later%20stitched%20crucial%20partnerships%20with%20Axar%20Patel%20(47)%20and%20Shivam%20Dube%20(27)%20to%20propel%20India%20to%20176%2F7%20in%20their%2020%20overs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDefending%20176%2C%20Jasprit%20Bumrah%20provided%20India%20an%20early%20breakthrough%20as%20he%20cleaned%20up%20Reeza%20Hendricks%20(4)%20with%20a%20sensational%20delivery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArshdeep%20Singh%20later%20bagged%20the%20huge%20wicket%20of%20captain%20Aiden%20Markram%20(4)%20to%20reduce%20South%20Africa%20to%2012%2F2.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWicketkeeper-batter%20Quinton%20de%20Kock%20(39)%20and%20Tristan%20Stubbs%20(31)%20then%20stitched%20a%20crucial%2058-run%20stand%20to%20bring%20the%20Proteas%20back%20into%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeft-arm%20spinner%20Axar%20Patel%20ended%20the%20partnership%20as%20he%20castled%20Stubbs%20(31)%20before%20Arshdeep%20removed%20de%20Kock%20(39).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBatting%20at%20No.5%2C%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%20later%20slammed%20a%20blitzkrieg%20fifty%20to%20put%20South%20Africa%20in%20a%20great%20position.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Hardik%20Pandya%20dismissed%20Klaasen%20(52)%20in%20the%2017th%20over%20to%20change%20the%20fortune%20in%20India's%20favour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20other%20end%2C%20Bumrah%20continued%20his%20brilliant%20spell%20as%20he%20removed%20Marco%20Jansen%20(2).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20South%20Africa%20needed%2016%20off%20the%20final%20over%2C%20Pandya%20bagged%20the%20huge%20wicket%20of%20David%20Miller%20(21)%20courtesy%20of%20an%20incredible%20catch%20by%20Suryakumar%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPandya%20later%20kept%20his%20calm%20to%20guide%20India%20to%20their%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20nail-biting%20win%2C%20we%20take%20a%20look%20at%20five%20points%20that%20helped%20India%20clinch%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20in%20the%20West%20Indies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EJasprit%20Bumrah's%20match-defining%20spell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJasprit%20Bumrah%20produced%20a%20spell%20for%20the%20ages%20to%20help%20India%20clinch%20their%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20after%2017%20years.%20With%2030%20required%20off%2030%20balls%2C%20Rohit%20Sharma%20once%20again%20showed%20his%20faith%20in%20Bumrah.%20The%20India's%20bowling%20spearhead%20responded%20as%20he%20conceded%20just%20four%20runs%20in%20the%2016th%20over%20and%20later%20gave%20away%20only%20two%20runs%20in%20the%2018th%20over%20including%20picking%20up%20Jansen's%20wicket%20to%20pull%20things%20for%20the%20Men%20in%20Blue.%20Bumrah%20ended%20with%20figures%20of%204-0-18-2%20to%20guide%20India%20to%20the%20coveted%20title.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav's%20stunning%20catch%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESuryakumar%20Yadav%20took%20a%20breathtaking%20catch%20in%20the%20final%20over%20of%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20final%20as%20he%20played%20a%20pivotal%20role%20in%20helping%20India%20clinch%20the%20title.%20As%20South%20Africa%20needed%2016%20off%20the%20final%20six%20deliveries%2C%20Pandya%20removed%20the%20dangerous%20David%20Miller%20after%20he%20miscued%20a%20huge%20hit%20over%20long%20off.%20Suryakumar%20later%20produced%20an%20incredible%20fielding%20effort%20to%20help%20dismiss%20Miller%20and%20claim%20a%20crucial%20wicket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EAxar%20Patel's%20all-round%20effort%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAxar%20Patel%20was%20one%20of%20the%20standout%20performers%20for%20India%20in%20their%20thrilling%20win%20over%20South%20Africa.%20Reeling%20at%2034%2F3%2C%20Axar%20stitched%20an%20important%20partnership%20with%20Kohli%20to%20bring%20India%20back%20into%20the%20game.%20Axar%20and%20Kohli%20forged%20a%2072-run%20stand%20for%20the%20fourth%20wicket%20before%20he%20departed%20in%20an%20unfortunate%20run-out.%20The%20southpaw%20scored%2047%20off%2031%20balls%2C%20laced%20with%20one%20four%20and%20four%20sixes.%20Later%2C%20Axar%20also%20contributed%20with%20the%20bowl%20and%20claimed%20the%20huge%20wicket%20of%20Tristan%20Stubbs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EVirat%20Kohli's%20match-winning%20fifty%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20played%20another%20match-winning%20knock%20as%20he%20helped%20India%20post%20a%20fighting%20total%20at%20the%20Kensington%20Oval%20in%20Bridgetown%2C%20Barbados.%20While%20Kohli%20was%20short%20on%20runs%20heading%20into%20the%20final%2C%20the%20Indian%20talisman%20once%20again%20rose%20to%20the%20occasion%20when%20the%20team%20needed%20the%20most.%20After%20India%20were%20reduced%20to%2034%2F3%2C%20Kohli%20established%20important%20partnerships%20with%20Axar%20and%20Dube%20to%20guide%20India%20to%20over%20170.%20Kohli%20scored%2059-ball%2076%20which%20included%20six%20fours%20and%20two%20sixes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHardik%20Pandya's%20crucial%20spell%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStar%20all-rounder%20Hardik%20Pandya%20provided%20India%20with%20crucial%20breakthroughs%20throughout%20the%20match%20to%20help%20them%20defend%20176%20against%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20final.%20After%20the%20Indian%20spin%20duo%20of%20Axar%20Patel%20(1%2F49)%20and%20Kuldeep%20Yadav%20(0%2F45)%20were%20expensive%20on%20the%20day%2C%20the%20Rohit%20Sharma-led%20side%20needed%20someone%20to%20step%20up%20with%20the%20ball.%20Hardik%20was%20given%20the%20responsibility%20and%20he%20grabbed%20it%20with%20both%20hands.%20The%20right-arm%20pacer%20first%20bagged%20the%20massive%20wicket%20of%20Heinrich%20Klaasen%20and%20later%20removed%20David%20Miller%20and%20Kagiso%20Rabada%20in%20the%20final%20over%20of%20the%20game%20to%20finish%20with%20figures%20of%203-0-20-3.%20Hardik's%20impressive%20spell%20was%20one%20of%20the%20standout%20performances%20that%20guided%20India%20to%20their%20second%20T20%20World%20Cup%20title%20after%2017%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719690960000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fk2fjidvg_india-t20-wc_625x300_30_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fhow-india-defeated-south-africa-in-t20-world-cup-2024-final-five-turning-points-5999260%