2%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A174%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Farticles%2Fcye0g5l2d5xo%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-bbc-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Farticles%2Fcye0g5l2d5xo.amp%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fsport%2Fcricket%2Farticles%2Fcye0g5l2d5xo.amp%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20Retires%20From%20T20Is%20After%20India's%20T20%20World%20Cup%20Triumph%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%2C%20former%20Indian%20cricket%20team%20captain%20and%20Player%20of%20the%20Match%20in%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%202024%20final%2C%20announced%20his%20retirement%20from%20the%20format%20right%20after%20India's%20historic%20win%20over%20South%20Africa%20in%20the%20title%20clash%20in%20Barbados%20on%20Saturday.%20Kohli%2C%20who%20has%20been%20one%20of%20India's%20best-ever%20cricketers%2C%20said%20that%20it%20was%20time%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20to%20take%20over.%20For%20a%20boy%20who%20rose%20from%20the%20by-lanes%20of%20Delhi%20to%20rule%20world%20cricket%2C%20it%20was%20the%20perfect%20culmination%20of%20a%20T20I%20career%20that%20saw%20several%20highs%20as%20well%20as%20lows%20as%20captain.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20was%20my%20last%20T20%20World%20Cup%2C%20this%20is%20exactly%20what%20we%20wanted%20to%20achieve%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kohli%20told%20the%20broadcasters%20after%20India%20ended%20a%2011-ear%20ICC%20title%20drought.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COne%20day%20you%20feel%20like%20you%20can't%20get%20a%20run%20and%20this%20happens%2C%20God%20is%20great.%20(It%20is)%20just%20the%20occasion%2C%20now%20or%20never%20kind%20of%20situation.%20This%20was%20my%20last%20T20%20game%20playing%20for%20India.%20We%20wanted%20to%20lift%20that%20cup.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%20I%20have%2C%20this%20was%20an%20open%20secret%20(retirement).%20Not%20something%20that%20I%20wasn't%20going%20to%20announce%20even%20if%20we%20had%20lost.%20Time%20for%20the%20next%20generation%20to%20take%20the%20T20%20game%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kohli%20confirmed%20when%20asked%20by%20Harsha%20Bhogle%20if%20he%20was%20making%20the%20official%20announcement%20about%20him%20calling%20it%20a%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt's%20been%20a%20long%20wait%20for%20us%2C%20waiting%20to%20win%20an%20ICC%20tournament.%20You%20look%20at%20someone%20like%20Rohit%20(Sharma)%2C%20he's%20played%209%20T20%20World%20Cups%20and%20this%20is%20my%20sixth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHe%20deserves%20it.%20It's%20been%20difficult%20to%20hold%20things%20(emotions)%20back%20and%20I%20think%20it's%20going%20to%20sink%20in%20later.%20It's%20an%20amazing%20day%20and%20I'm%20thankful%2C%E2%80%9D%20Kohli%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVirat%20Kohli%20is%20one%20of%20those%20rare%20cricketers%20who%20have%20won%20both%20the%20ODI%20and%20the%20T20%20World%20Cup%20now.%20Kohli%20played%20his%20first%20T20I%20in%202010%20and%20then%20went%20on%20to%20play%20several%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20But%20every%20time%2C%20India%20fell%20short%20until%20the%202024%20edition%2C%20where%20Kohli%20emerged%20as%20a%20saviour%20after%20India's%20horrendous%20start%20against%20South%20Africa.%20He%20scored%20a%20gritty%2076%20off%2059%20balls%20as%20India%20scored%20a%20record%20high%20total%20of%20176%2F7%20in%20a%20T20%20World%20Cup%20final.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20his%20glorious%20career%2C%20Virat%20Kohli%20finished%20with%20a%20tally%20of%204188%20in%20125%20matches%20at%20an%20average%20of%2048.69.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719686940000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Fg6m2jbfg_virat-kohli_625x300_29_June_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Ft20-world-cup-2024%2Fvirat-kohli-announces-retirement-from-t20is-after-indias-t20-world-cup-triumph-5998997%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Virat%20Kohli%20announces%20retirement%20from%20T20%20Internationals%20after%20India's%20T20%20