.%20Team%20India%20have%20won%2041%20out%20of%2056%20ODIs%2C%2048%20out%20of%2069%20T20Is%2C%20and%20lost%20just%20one%20Test%20series%2C%20winning%20five%20and%20drawing%20two.%20In%20all%20formats%2C%20India's%20form%20has%20been%20dominant%20and%20a%20cut%20above%20any%20other%20team%20on%20earth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202023%2C%20India%20walked%20to%20the%20Asia%20Cup%20title.%20And%20in%202024%2C%20Dravid's%20India%20held%20the%20No.%201%20spot%20in%20the%20teams'%20rankings%20in%20all%20three%20formats%2C%20an%20unprecedented%20first%20in%20Indian%20cricket%20history.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20home%2C%20Australia%20and%20England%20have%20been%20no%20match%20for%20India.%20Away%20from%20home%2C%20India%20took%20the%20fight%20to%20England%20and%20South%20Africa%2C%20with%20two%20drawn%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20hurt%20of%20lost%20Finals%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E2023%20proved%20to%20be%20a%20year%20of%20hurt%20for%20India%2C%20as%20the%20World%20Test%20championship%20and%20ODI%20World%20Cup%20campaigns%20ended%20in%20pain%20in%20the%20Final.%20The%20two%20tournaments%20remain%20rare%20black%20spots%20in%20a%20shining%20era%20of%20Team%20India%20under%20Rahul%20Dravid.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20reality%2C%20the%20pain%20of%20the%20lost%20finals%20shows%20the%20level%20of%20dominance%20that%20Dravid's%20India%20managed%20to%20hit.%20India%20were%20nearly%20unbeaten%20in%20the%202023%20World%20Cup%20and%20unbeaten%20in%20the%202024%20T20%20World%20Cup.%20It%20says%20something%20when%20a%20semi-final%20in%20the%202022%20T20%20World%20Cup%20is%20the%20worst%20India%20has%20done%20in%20a%20major%20ICC%20tournament%20in%20this%20period.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20anything%2C%20Dravid's%20era%20should%20be%20celebrated%20as%20one%20of%20India's%20finest%20periods%2C%20and%20not%20be%20looked%20back%20on%20with%20the%20hurt%20of%20lost%20finals.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ETransition%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Rohit%20Sharma%5C%22%20