s%20year%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-is-retiring-patriot-missile-systems-that-could-help-ukraine-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshutting%20down%20its%20aging%20Patriot%20batteries%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20replacing%20them%20with%20more%20advanced%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIsrael%20has%20never%20been%20impressed%20with%20its%20versions%20of%20the%20Patriot%20system%2C%20having%20seen%20them%20struggle%20in%20combat%20against%20Iraqi%20Scud%20missiles%20fired%20at%20its%20cities%20in%201991%2C%20as%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fisrael-is-retiring-patriot-missile-systems-that-could-help-ukraine-2024-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20previously%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOfficials%20estimated%20that%20it%20shot%20down%20only%20one%20or%20possibly%20even%20none%20of%20the%20missiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIsrael%20has%20long%20been%20looking%20for%20a%20more%20advanced%20and%20more%20indigenous%20system%20to%20supplement%20or%20replace%20the%20Patriot%2C%20not%20only%20given%20its%20service%20history%20but%20also%20the%20supply%20chain%20that%20it%20requires%2C%26quot%3B%20Ryan%20Bohl%2C%20a%20senior%20Middle%20East%20and%20North%20Africa%20analyst%20at%20the%20risk%20intelligence%20company%20RANE%2C%20told%20BI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20Israel%20views%20the%20Patriot%20as%20out%20of%20date%20and%20too%20expensive%20to%20keep%20up%20with%20given%20the%20breakthroughs%20that%20were%20demonstrated%20during%20that%20barrage%20by%20newer%20systems%2C%26quot%3B%20Bohl%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Israel%20has%20yet%20to%20fully%20retire%20its%20Patriot%20systems%2C%20as%20it%20is%20still%20using%20them%20in%20the%20ongoing%20conflict%20with%20Hamas%20and%20would%20likely%20want%20them%20should%20an%20all-out%20war%20with%20the%20Lebanese%20militant%20group%20Hezbollah%20break%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-