0b021b5cae8f366%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20burgers%20were%20stacked%20neatly%20on%20top%20of%20one%20another%2C%20with%20the%20toppings%20under%20the%20beef.%20We%20thought%20this%20was%20interesting%20%E2%80%94%20we%20usually%20place%20burger%20toppings%20on%20top%20of%20the%20patties%20to%20prevent%20the%20bottom%20bun%20from%20getting%20soggy.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThis%20burger%20tasted%20strongly%20of%20mustard%2C%20but%20we%20enjoyed%20the%20classic%20toppings.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Chili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20w%2FCheese%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679d76150b021b5cae8f362%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChili's%20Double%20Oldtimer%20with%20cheese.%3Cp%3EErin%20McDowell%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EA%20thin%20slice%20of%20cheese%20separated%20the%20two%20burger%20patties%2C%20and%20we%20thought%20the%20lettuce%20and%20tomato%20tasted%20fresh.%20However%2C%20we%20had%20mixed%20feelings%20about%20the%20mustard.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20mustard%20almost%20overpowered%20the%20other%20ingredients%2C%20and%20the%20additional%20patty%20made%20the%20burger%20so%20juicy%20that%20the%20bread%20was%20nearly%20flattened.%20Still%2C%20we%20thought%20the%20burger%20patties%20were%20cooked%20perfectly%20and%20had%20an%20excellent%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20a%20great%20classic%20burger%2C%20similar%20to%20one%20we%20might%20make%20at%20a%20cookout.%20However%2C%20we%20all%20agreed%20that%20when%20dining%20out%2C%20we%20prefer%20to%20choose%20more%20creative%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20also%20tried%20the%20single-patty%20Oldtimer%20burger%20without%20cheese.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22403