%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC2askr1SZC6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20video%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20two%20women%20walk%20into%20the%20school%20in%20their%20white%2C%20floor-length%20gowns%2C%20accessorized%20with%20their%20backpacks%20and%20water%20bottles.%20Their%20colleagues%20can%20be%20heard%20laughing%20and%20cheering%2C%20and%20one%20yells%20out%2C%20%26quot%3BOh%20yes!%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOsmundson%20thinks%20the%20experience%20teaches%20a%20good%20lesson.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYour%20students%20are%20going%20to%20gain%20a%20lot%20of%20excitement%20from%20what%20you%20do%2C%20but%20just%20don't%20be%20scared%20to%20do%20things%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BA%20lot%20of%20the%20time%2C%20what%20you%20build%20up%20in%20your%20head%20is%20a%20fleeting%20thought%20in%20other%20people's%20minds.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20an%20unexpected%20bonding%20moment%20with%20two%20other%20staff%20members%20who%20were%20wearing%20bridesmaids'%20dresses.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%20even%20though%20things%20can%20be%20intimidating%2C%20I%20think%20doing%20things%20that%20sometimes%20scare%20us%20or%20might%20embarrass%20us%20are%20still%20worth%20a%20try%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227c0257f4-2180-4d69-bfb5-6f420ea33a42%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EReusing%20and%20preserving%20a%20costly%20item%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%3Fh%3Dd6c1028a8bf3747498782ca0705ae5838d8a2ddac484386a1d57e036800b1781%26postID%3D6627f531d541c16b97074981%26postSlug%3Dteachers-rewear-wedding-dresses-to-school-2024-6%26site%3Dbi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.theknot.com%252Fcontent%252Fwedding-data-insights%252Freal-weddings-study%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20The%20Knot%20Real%20Weddings%20Study%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20surveyed%20nearly%2010%2C000%20US%20couples%20who%20g