awn%20back%20in%20amid%20this%20year's%20RoaringKitty-fueled%20rally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20he%20posted%2C%20I%20kind%20of%20dabbled%20into%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20BI.%20%26quot%3BYou%20see%20all%20the%20hype%20around%20it%2C%20and%20then%20you%20see%20the%20price%20just%20shoot%20up.%20It's%20hard%20not%20to%20want%20to%20just%20jump%20in.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20allure%20of%20GameStop%20stock%20has%20been%20the%20potential%20for%20a%20big%2C%20quick%20payday%2C%20Brian%20added%2C%20and%20plowing%20cash%20into%20a%20meme%20stock%20is%20like%20buying%20a%20lotto%20ticket%20for%20a%20chance%20at%20financial%20independence.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B%5BThey%5D%20could%20essentially%20just%20make%20you%20financially%20free.%20You%20never%20have%20to%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20live%20in%20the%20Bay%20area%20of%20California%2C%20so%20it's%20very%20hard%20out%20here%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20very%20well-paid%20job%20or%20if%20you%20don't%20have%20a%20dual%20income%20%E2%80%A6%20So%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20something%20that%20could%20gain%20me%20the%20freedom%20to%20not%20have%20to%20work%20and%20grind%20it%20out%20every%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOthers%20echoed%20that%20sentiment%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20chance%20to%20hit%20it%20big%20is%20too%20enticing%20to%20sit%20it%20out%20as%20the%20stock%20starts%20going%20parabolic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI've%20been%20unemployed%20since%20November%20and%20I've%20been%20struggling%20to%20find%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Zaine%2C%20another%20retail%20trader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20never%20traded%20meme%20stocks%20but%20has%20bet%20against%20risky%20assets%20during%20the%20pandemic.%20His%20portfolio%20ballooned%20to%20as%20much%20as%20%2475%2C000%20before%20plunging%20to%20near%20zero%2C%20screenshots%20of%20his%20brokerage%20account%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20go%20to%20these%20outlets%20thinking%2C%20I%20can%20just%20make%20a%20little%20bit%20of%20money%20on%20the%20side%20to%20kind%20of%20just%20survive%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20it%20ends%20up%20being%20this%20snowball%20effect%20that%2C%20if%20you%20don't%20look%20at%20yourself%20in%20the%20mirror%2C%20you%20can%20really%20end%20up%20losing%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgamestop-roaring-kitty-gme-stock-price-rally-meme-traders-wallstreetbets-2024-6%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719664202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6679aaef40cf2af6e4f5196b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fgamestop-roaring-kitty-gme-stock-price-rally-meme-traders-wallstreetbets-2024-6%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Retail%20traders%20who%20lost%20money%20in%20the%20first%20GameStop%20saga%20say%20that%20they're%20still%20tempted%20to%20jump%20back%20in%20as%20the%20stock%20rallies%20anew%20in%202024.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22jsor%40businessinsider.com%20(Jennifer%20Sor)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A102%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fmarkets.businessinsider.com%2Fnews%2Fstocks%2Fgamestop-roaring-kitty-gme-stock-price-rally-meme-traders-wallstreetbets-2024-6%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Significant%20progress%20in%20SDGs%2C%20yet%20challenges%20remain%3A%20Mospi%20report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719661984000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-03%2F22%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F400X400%2F1711100047-729.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fsignificant-progress-in-sdgs-yet-challenges-remain-mospi-report-124062900474_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Report%20highlights%20gains%20in%20health%2C%20education%3B%20gaps%20remain%20in%20wage%20equality%2C%20waste%22%2C%22a