0past%20three%20years%2C%20she%20claims%20to%20have%20received%20a%20production%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20of%20tomato%20per%20acre%2C%20resulting%20in%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20in%20the%20previous%20financial%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EThis%20is%20why%20you%20should%20grow%20vegetables!%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETraditional%20crops%20like%20rice%20and%20wheat%20have%20longer%20growth%20cycles%20which%20are%20generally%20twice%20a%20year.%20Vegetable%20farming%2C%20however%2C%20gives%20multiple%20harvests%20as%20the%20growth%20cycles%20are%20shorter%20and%20are%20more%20profitable.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CVegetable%20farming%20offers%20a%20triple%20win%20%E2%80%93%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351525%2Ffarming-profitable-how-to-make-natural-pesticides-himachal-couple-zero-budget-natural-earns-double%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehigher%20income%20for%20farmers%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20traders%2C%20enhanced%20consumer%20health%20and%20a%20rejuvenated%20economy.%20In%20other%20words%2C%20when%20vegetables%20rise%2C%20people%20thrive%2C%E2%80%9D%20Dilip%20Rajan%2C%20the%20chief%20operating%20officer%20at%20the%20East-West%20Seed%20Global%20told%20the%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmarika%20realised%20this%20fact%20and%20first%20worked%20on%20getting%20the%20land%20ready%20for%20vegetable%20cultivation.%20The%20first%20vegetable%20she%20grew%20was%20tomato%2C%20seeking%20help%20from%20an%20agricultural%20consultant%20to%20make%20the%20transition%20smooth.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201599px)%20100vw%2C%201599px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221599%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20has%20harvested%20tomato%20in%20over%2013%20acres.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343.jpeg%201599w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343-1536x1153.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika2-1719549343-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354724%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmarika%20has%20grown%20tomato%20in%20over%2013%20acres.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20first%20focused%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351690%2Fyash-dayal-sharma-fertile-beeghas-organic-waste-vermicompost-stubble-burning-train-farmers-soil-health%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eimproving%20the%20soil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20adding%20cow%20dung%20and%20vermicompost.%20We%20just%20left%20the%20soil%20free%20for%20a%20few%20months%2C%20basking%20in%20the%20sunlight.%20We%20installed%20fences%20and%20ensured%20that%20the%20drainage%20system%20was%20in%20place%20and%20the%20land%20was%20sloping%2C%E2%80%9D%20Smarika%20shares%20with%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20installed%20a%20drip%20irrigation%20system.%20After%20this%2C%20she%20prepared%20a%20raised%20bed%20for%20tomatoes%20and%20mulches%20(a%20layer%20of%20material%20applied%20to%20the%20surface%20of%20an%20area%20of%20soil%20to%20conserve%20soil%20moisture%20and%20improve%20fertility).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20experimenting%20and%20researching%20over%20the%20weekends%20between%202019%20and%202021%2C%20Smarika%20took%20the%20plunge%20into%20full-time%20farming.%20With%20seeds%20purchased%20from%20a%20local%20nursery%2C%20the%20Chandrakar%20family%20prepared%20for%20their%20first%20tomato%20harvest%20in%202021.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20received%20a%20great%20harvest%20of%20almost%2050%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20in%20the%20first%20year.%20We%20sold%20it%20in%20local%20%3Cem%3Emandis%3C%2Fem%3E%20(marts)%20and%20in%20other%20cities%20like%20Visakhapatnam%2C%20Patna%2C%20Kolkata%2C%20New%20Delhi%2C%20Bengaluru%20and%20more.%20I%20have%20tied-up%20with%20brokers%20with%20whom%20I%20pre-decide%20the%20rates%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBesides%20tomatoes%2C%20she%20also%20grows%20bottle%20gourd%2C%20cucumber%20and%20brinjal.%20The%20sowing%20and%20harvesting%20season%20is%20between%20May%20to%20March%2C%20with%20the%20cycle%20roughly%20around%20three%20months%2C%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20we%20would%20only%20be%20able%20to%20harvest%20paddy%20twice%20a%20year%2C%20we%20are%20able%20to%20harvest%20vegetables%20many%20more%20times.%20It%E2%80%99s%20also%20much%20more%20profitable%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20same%20%3Cem%3EEconomic%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%20article%2C%20Dilip%20Rajan%20shared%2C%20%E2%80%9CFor%20instance%2C%20a%20thousand%20square%20metres%20of%20land%20planted%20with%20bitter%20gourd%20will%20give%20a%20farmer%20roughly%20the%20same%20income%20as%20one%20hectare%20planted%20for%20rice.%20Vegetables%20can%20be%20harvested%20quickly%20(45-55%20days)%2C%20and%203-4%20crops%20can%20be%20cultivated%20throughout%20the%20year%20to%20meet%20the%20increased%20demand%20for%20vegetables%20and%20changes%20in%20food%20consumption.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFarming%20is%20a%20viable%20career%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20the%20past%20three%20years%2C%20Smarika%20has%20been%20cultivating%20a%20variety%20of%20vegetables%20on%20her%20land.%20She%20now%20plans%20to%20add%2015%20acres%20more%20this%20year%20to%20her%20existing%2020.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Smarika%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20area%20under%20vegetable%20cultivation.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058.jpeg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-300x225.jpeg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-500x375.jpeg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-768x576.jpeg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-1536x1152.jpeg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fsmarika3-1719550058-150x113.jpeg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354729%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESmarika%20plans%20to%20expand%20the%20area%20under%20vegetable%20cultivation.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CLast%20year%2C%20we%20received%20a%20harvest%20of%2055%20tonnes%20per%20acre%20for%20tomatoes.%20With%20this%2C%20our%20turnover%20was%20over%20Rs%201.5%20crore%20in%20FY%2023-24%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESmarika%20runs%20the%20farm%20along%20with%20her%20brother%20and%20father.%20Employing%20over%20125%20people%20on%20the%20farm%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20use%20better%20technology%20going%20ahead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CCurrently%2C%20we%20are%20doing%20a%20lot%20of