Chhattisgarh.%20With%20125%20people%20employed%20in%20her%20fields%2C%20she%20hopes%20to%20introduce%20advanced%20technology%20to%20improve%20productivity.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354716%2Fvegetable-farmer-smarika-chandrakar-grows-tomatoes-cucumbers-brinjals-in-chhattisgarh-farming-mba-grad-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Homemaker%20to%20Entrepreneur%3A%20Woman%20Found%20Financial%20Freedom%20in%20Coconut%20Biz%2C%20Earns%20Rs%2020%20Lakh%2FMonth%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CNever%20in%20my%20wildest%20dream%20did%20I%20ever%20think%20of%20becoming%20an%20entrepreneur.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20have%20any%20experience%20in%20the%20business%20field%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Sumila%20Jayaraj%2C%20the%20founder%20of%20Greenaura%2C%20a%20company%20which%20sells%20coconut-based%20products%20across%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHailing%20from%20the%20small%20town%20of%20Engandiyur%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Sumila%E2%80%99s%20childhood%20aspiration%20was%20to%20become%20a%20doctor.%20However%2C%20after%20graduating%20in%20zoology%2C%20she%20studied%20English%20Literature%20and%20was%20married%20before%20the%20results%20were%20even%20announced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20her%20marriage%2C%20she%20moved%20to%20Mumbai%20with%20her%20husband.%20%E2%80%9CSoon%2C%20I%20gave%20birth%20to%20twins%2C%20becoming%20an%20extremely%20occupied%20homemaker%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAfter%20six%20years%2C%20we%20shifted%20to%20Kerala%20when%20my%20husband%20went%20to%20Dubai%20for%20a%20job.%20My%20kids%20also%20moved%20out%20for%20studies.%20I%20had%20enough%20time%20on%20my%20hands%20and%20wanted%20to%20engage%20myself%20in%20work.%20I%20felt%20this%20was%20the%20right%20time%20when%20I%20could%20establish%20an%20identity%20for%20myself%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202010%2C%