0regrets%20don%E2%80%99t%20exist%20for%20mere%20humans%20like%20us%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Col%20start%3D%5C%223%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3EBe%20mindful%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fol%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDo%20something%20that%20connects%20you%20to%20something%20bigger%20than%20your%20goal.%20%E2%80%9CMeditate%2C%20take%20a%20walk%20in%20nature%2C%20sit%20under%20the%20moon%2C%20listen%20to%20birds%20and%20so%20on.%20This%20reminds%20you%20that%20your%20goals%20are%20not%20the%20ultimate%20objective%20but%20merely%20a%20part%20of%20the%20bigger%20plan.%20It%20keeps%20you%20grounded.%20Any%20type%20of%20meditation%20or%20journaling%20keeps%20you%20sane%20during%20this%20hard%20phase%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201600px)%20100vw%2C%201600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221600%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taruni's%20hand-drawn%20timetable%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806.jpg%201600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-1536x1152.jpg%201536w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIMG-20240625-WA0119-1719379806-150x113.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354346%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ETaruni%E2%80%99s%20hand-drawn%20timetable.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3