lockquote%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-quote%20wp-block-quote-is-layout-flow%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%E2%80%9CWhile%20plastic%20straws%2C%20bags%2C%20and%20bottles%20are%20widely%20discussed%2C%20items%20like%20pens%20are%20rarely%20mentioned.%20However%2C%20the%20plastic%20waste%20from%20pens%20is%20substantial%2C%20comparable%20to%2050%20percent%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F187780%2Fbengaluru-woman-initiative-shop-vendors-ditch-plastic-bags-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplastic%20straw%20%3C%2Fa%3Eproblem.%20The%20lack%20of%20discussion%20around%20this%20issue%20was%20striking%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20realised%20there%20were%20no%20real%20alternatives%20to%20plastic%20pens.%20Some%20efforts%20reduced%20the%20plastic%20content%20by%2050%2C%2070%2C%20or%20even%2088%20percent%2C%20but%20plastic%20was%20still%20present.%20Tests%20showed%20that%20even%20pens%20with%20paper%20bodies%20and%20plastic%20cores%20acted%20like%20laminated%20paper%20cups%2C%20preventing%20full%20biodegradability.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20shares%20why%20it%20is%20important%20to%20make%20sustainable%20stationery.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20problem%20we%20faced%20was%20that%2095%20percent%20of%20a%20pen%20is%20composed%20of%20non-biodegradable%20materials%2C%20primarily%20plastic%20and%20metal%20mixtures.%20These%20plastics%20are%20often%20different%20types%2C%20such%20as%20PVC%2C%20and%20polycarbonate%2C%20each%20with%20different%20properties.%20The%20damage%20caused%20by%20these%20materials%20is%20significant%20because%20the%20components%20can%E2%80%99t%20be%20easily%20disassembled%20and%20recycled%20separately%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20no%20economic%20value%20in%20recycling%20them%2C%20making%20it%20practically%20impossible%20to%20recycle%20these%20pens.%20Consequently%2C%20they%20won%E2%80%99t%20biodegrade%20for%20the%20next%20300%20years%20or%20more.%20This%20amplifies%20the%20problem%3A%20with%20an%20annual%20production%20volume%20of%2050%20billion%20pens%2C%20all%20of%20this%20plastic%20waste%20cannot%20be%20recycled%20and%20won%E2%80%99t%20biodegrade%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20reiterates.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-3-1719320232.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22It%20took%20Saurabh%20and%20his%20team%20almost%20two%20years%20to%20design%20the%20pen.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-3-1719320232.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-3-1719320232-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-3-1719320232-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-3-1719320232-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-3-1719320232-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354253%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EIt%20took%20Saurabh%20and%20his%20team%20almost%20two%20years%20to%20design%20the%20pen.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnlike%20plastic%20bottles%2C%20pen%20plastics%20are%20problematic.%20While%20PET%20bottle%20recycling%20rates%20are%20not%20perfect%2C%20they%20exist%20and%20are%20improving.%20In%20contrast%2C%20there%20is%20currently%20no%20effective%20recycling%20solution%20for%20pen%20plastics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20why%20we%20invested%20significant%20time%20and%20effort%20into%20finding%20alternatives.%20We%20experimented%20with%20various%20materials%20and%20methods%20to%20replace%20plastic.%20Our%20solution%20involves%20using%20recycled%20paper%20and%20vegetable%20oil.%20The%20vegetable%20oil%20acts%20as%20a%20barrier%20between%20the%20ink%20and%20the%20paper%2C%20providing%20the%20necessary%20functionality%20without%20relying%20on%20plastic%2C%20shares%20Saurabh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20body%20of%20the%20pen%20is%20made%20of%20bamboo%20and%20the%20cap%20is%20made%20of%20coconut%20shell%20%E2%80%94%20this%20simple%20yet%20effective%20approach%20has%20allowed%20him%20to%20create%20pens%20that%20are%20both%20sustainable%20and%20functional.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20experimented%20from%202018%20to%202020%20before%20finally%20narrowing%20down%20to%20one%20design.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20tried%20various%20methods%20to%20reduce%20and%20eliminate%20plastic%20in%20pens.%20We%20conducted%20numerous%20trials%2C%20each%20requiring%20extensive%20testing%20for%20shelf%20life%2C%20which%20must%20be%2018%20months.%20Each%20test%20took%20around%20six%20months%20to%20yield%20results%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CFinally%2C%20in%20January%20this%20year%2C%20we%20achieved%20a%20breakthrough.%20Our%20current%20method%20allows%20us%20to%20produce%20pens%20with%20an%2018-month%20shelf%20life%20without%20plastic.%20This%20marks%20a%20significant%20milestone%20in%20our%20journey%20toward%20sustainable%20stationery%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECurrently%2C%20the%20pens%20are%20available%20for%20bulk%20purchase%20by%20businesses.%20So%20far%2C%20he%20has%20sold%2020%2C000%20pens%20and%20hopes%20to%20increase%20this%20number%20in%20the%20future.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAditya%20Pratap%20Singh%2C%20who%20is%20a%20sports%20professional%20and%20a%20team%20member%20of%20Youth%20For%20Climate%20India%2C%20used%20the%20biodegradable%20pen.%20%E2%80%9CBeing%20an%20environment%20advocate%2C%20climate%20change%20and%20plastic%20pollution%20deeply%20concern%20me.%20I%20have%20a%20bag%20full%20of%20refills%20of%20pens%20that%20I%20used.%20While%20the%20problem%20seems%20small%2C%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20an%20alternative.%20When%20I%20found%20out%20about%20Saurabh%E2%80%99s%20innovation%2C%20I%20was%20intrigued%20and%20bought%20two%20pens%20from%20him%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-4-1719320374.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%2295%20percent%20of%20a%20pen%20is%20plastic%20with%20no%20use%20other%20than%20holding%20the%20ink.%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-4-1719320374.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-4-1719320374-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-4-1719320374-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-4-1719320374-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-4-1719320374-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354259%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESaurabh%20shares%20that%2095%20percent%20of%20a%20pen%20is%20plastic%20with%20no%20use%20other%20than%20holding%20the%20ink.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20just%20opened%20one%20of%20them%20to%20see%20if%20there%20was%20really%20zero%20use%20of%20plastic.%20It%20was%20true%2C%20he%20used%20materials%20like%20bamboo%20and%20coconut%20shells%20but%20no%20plastic.%20The%20pen%2C%20to%20be%20precise%2C%20feels%20exactly%20like%20any%20other%20pen.%20You%20won%E2%80%99t%20even%20feel%20a%20difference%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESaurabh%20informs%20that%20the%20price%20of%20the%20pen%20currently%20starts%20from%20Rs%2030%20and%20goes%20up%20to%20Rs%20300.%20%E2%80%9CHowever%2C%20I%20am%20currently%20working%20on%20making%20it%20available%20at%20competitive%20prices%20as%20plastic-based%20pens%20to%20make%20it%20available%20to%20the%20masses%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20remarks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20believe%20that%20if%20there%20is%20an%20alternative%20available%20for%20people%20to%20use%2C%20they%20will%20opt%20for%20it.%20While%20a%20pen%20might%20sound%20like%20a%20small%20thing%2C%20if%20you%20look%20at%20the%20bigger%20picture%2C%20even%20small%20efforts%20matter%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Edited%20by%20Pranita%20Bhat%3B%20All%20Images%20Credit%3A%20Saurabh)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1719322159000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2Fbio-pen-2-1719320147.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D354235%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Noticing%20the%20lack%20of%20sustainable%20alternatives%20to%20plastic%20stationery%20in%20India%2C%20Delhi-based%20Saurabh%20H%20Mehta%20started%20NOTE%20(No%20Offence%20To%20Earth)%20to%20develop%20a%20biodegradable%20pen.%20He%20has%20sold%20over%2020%2C000%20units%20so%20far.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Tina%20Freese%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A18%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354235%2Fsaurabh-mehta-delhi-makes-biodegradable-pen-bamboo-coconut-oil-sustainable-stationery-no-plastic%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Suffered%20From%20Chickenpox%3F%20Here%E2%80%99s%20Why%20You%20Could%20Be%20at%20Risk%20of%20Shingles!%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20article%20is%20sponsored%20by%20GlaxoSmithKline%20Pharmaceuticals.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20last%20week%20of%20April%2C%20World%20Immunization%20Week%20is%20commemorated%20worldwide%20to%20celebrate%20the%20lifesaving%20power%20of%20vaccines.%20The%20ultimate%20objective%20of%20the%20event%20is%20to%20educate%20the%20public%20to%20protect%20themselves%20from%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20vaccination%20is%20often%20associated%20with%20childhood%2C%20it%20is%20also%20crucial%20for%20adults.%20Various%20research%20points%20to%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20immune%20system%20wanes%20as%20you%20age%3Csup%3E1%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20Gradually%2C%20its%20response%20to%20invading%20microbes%20slows%20down%2C%20and%20the%20body%20takes%20longer%20to%20recover%20due%20to%20fewer%20immune%20cells.%20Sadly%2C%20this%20increases%20the%20risk%20of%20contracting%20serious%20illnesses%20such%20as%20hepatitis%2C%20tetanus%2C%20shingles%20and%20more.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20you%20haven%E2%80%99t%20heard%20of%20shingles%2C%20then%20it%20is%20high%20time%20you%20know%20about%20it.%20Why%3F%20According%20to%20global%20data%2C%20one%20out%20of%20every%20three%20people%2050%20years%20and%20above%20may%20develop%20shingles%20in%20a%20lifetime%3Csup%3E2%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20So%2C%20it%20is%20important%20to%20arm%20yourself%20with%20information%20and%20stay%20protected%20than%20be%20taken%20by%20surprise.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20is%20Shingles%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECommonly%20known%20as%20%3Cem%3Eakki%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Edaapad%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20and%20%3Cem%3Enaagin%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20shingles%20is%20a%20viral%20infection%20caused%20by%20the%20varicella-zoster%20virus%20(VZV)%20%E2%80%94%20the%20same%20virus%20that%20causes%20chickenpox.%20This%20virus%20stays%20in%20the%20body%20and%20can%20reactivate%20later%20in%20life%20to%20cause%20shingles%3Csup%3E3%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20Now%20if%20you%20think%20about%20it%2C%20almost%20all%20of%20us%20have%20either%20experienced%20chickenpox%20or%20know%20of%20someone%20who%20has.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20what%20really%20is%20shingles%3F%20Shingles%20causes%20a%20painful%20rash%20that%20may%20appear%20as%20a%20stripe%20of%20blisters%3Csup%3E4%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20The%20early%20symptoms%20of%20shingles%20can%20manifest%20in%20the%20form%20of%20itching%2C%20tingling%2C%20burning%2C%20fever%2C%20body%20or%20headaches%3Csup%3E5%3C%2Fsup%3E%2C%20and%20pain%20over%20dermatome%20areas.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20pain%20of%20shingles%20can%20feel%20like%20electric%20shocks%2C%20nail%20piercing%2C%20and%20an%20unbearable%20burning%20sensation%3Csup%3E6%23%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20In%20some%20cases%2C%20the%20pain%20is%20said%20to%20be%20more%20painful%20than%20labour%20pain%20and%20can%20persist%20for%20even%20months%3Csup%3E7%3C%2Fsup%3E!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlthough%20it%20can%20occur%20at%20any%20age%2C%20the%20disease%20is%20most%20common%20among%20people%2050%20years%20or%20older%3Csup%3E8%3C%2Fsup%3E.%20And%20so%2C%20it%20is%20important%20for%20people%20to%20seek%20advice%20from%20healthcare%20professionals%20to%20understand%20the%20disease%20better%20and%20discuss%20its%20prevention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20504px)%20100vw%2C%20504px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286.png%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Shingles%20causes%20a%20painful%20rash%20that%20may%20appear%20as%20a%20stripe%20of%20blisters.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286.png%20504w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286-270x300.png%20270w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286-500x557.png%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F06%2FIn-betweeen-article-image_GSK-1-1719303286-150x167.png%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-354186%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22561%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EShingles%20causes%20a%20painful%20rash%20that%20may%20appear%20as%20a%20stripe%20of%20blisters.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20pursuit%20of%20good%20health%2C%20protect%20yourself%20from%20shingles%20to%20secure%20a%20happy%20future%20life%E2%80%9D%20says%2C%20Dr%20Sunil%20Kumar%20Gupta%2C%20MBBS%2C%20MD%2C%20DM%20(Medical%20Oncology)%2C%20Principal%20Director%20%26amp%3B%20HOD%20Haemato-Medical%20Oncology%20%26amp%3B%20BMT%20at%20Venkateshwar%20Hospital.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EMyths%20and%20misconceptions%20around%20shingles%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20lifetime%20prevalence%2C%20there%E2%80%99s%20a%20lack%20of%20awareness%20of%20shingles%20among%20people.%20In%202023%2C%20GlaxoSmithKline%20Pharmaceuticals%20(GSK)%20%E2%80%94%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20largest%20research-based%20pharmaceutical%20companies%20headquartered%20in%20London%20%E2%80%94%20conducted%20a%20global%20survey%3Csup%3E9%20%3C%2Fsup%3Eto%20find%20widespread%20misunderstandings%20about%20shingles.%20The%20online%20research%2C%20which%20surveyed%203%2C500%20adults%20aged%2050%20years%20across%2012%20countries%20%E2%80%94%20including%20China%2C%20the%20US%2C%20Germany%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20Australia%2C%20and%20India%2C%20assessed%20respondents%E2%80%99%20understanding%20of%20shingles%3Csup%3E9%3C%2Fsup%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20survey%20revealed%20that%2039%20percent%20of%20respondents%20believed%20that%20%E2%80%9Cyou%20can%E2%80%99t%20develop%20shingles%20if%20you%E2%80%99ve%20already%20had%20it%E2%80%9D.%20In%20fact%2C%20the%20survey%20also%20found%20that%2083.5%20percent%20of%20adults%20in%20India%20underestimate%20the%20risk%20of%20shingles%3Csup%3E10%3C%2Fsup%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDr%20Daniel%20Verdi%3Csup%3E11%3C%2Fsup%3E%2C%20a%20senior%20medical%20director%20at%20GSK%2C%20says%20the%20biggest%20misconception%20is%20that%20people%20living%20a%20healthy%20lifestyle%20believe%20they%20are%20not%20at%20risk.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20you%E2%80%99ve%20had%20chickenpox%20or%20even%20if%20you%E2%80%99re%20a%20healthy%2C%20active%20person%2C%20you%20are%20at%20risk%20for%20shingles.%20I%20encourage%20all%20adults%2050%20years%20and%20older%20to%20speak%20with%20their%20doctor%20to%20know%20more%20about%20how%20they%20can%20reduce%20their%20risk%20of%20shingles%20through%20vaccination%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20suggests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUnfortunately%2C%20there%20is%20no%20cure%20for%20shingles.%20However%2C%20treatment%20with%20antivirals%20to%20reduce%20the%20severity%20of%20the%20illness%2C%20antihistamines%20NSAIDs%2C%20and%20analgesics%20are%20used%20to%20comfort%20the%20patient.%20One%20of%20the%20best%20ways%20of%20shingles%20prevention%20is%20through%20vaccination%3Csup%3E12%3C%2Fsup%3E%20%E2%80%94%20developing%20the%20immune%20system%2C%20which%20helps%20fight%20the%20virus%20and%20prevents%20it%20from%20reactivating%3Csup%3E13%3C%2Fsup%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrevention%20is%20better%20than%20cure%20and%20it%20is%20important%20to%20at%20least%20protect%20yourself%20from%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases.%20So%2C%20consult%20your%20doctor%20and%20pledge%20to%20protect%20yourself%20and%20your%20family%20members%20from%20shingles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%23Individual%20patient%20symptoms%20of%20shingles%20may%20vary.%20These%20statements%20are%20based%20on%20some%20patient%E2%80%99s%20description%20of%20their%20shingles%20pain%20and%20do%20not%20represent%20every%20patient%E2%80%99s%20experience.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EA%20public%20awareness%20initiative%20by%20GlaxoSmithKline%20Pharmaceuticals%20Limited.%20Dr%20Annie%20Besant%20Road%2C%20Worli%2C%20Mumbai%20400%20030%2C%20India.%20Information%20appearing%20in%20this%20material%20is%20for%20general%20awareness%20only.%20Nothing%20contained%20in%20this%20material%20constitutes%20medical%20advice.%20Please%20consult%20your%20doctor%20for%20medical%20advice%20or%20any%20question%20or%20concern%20you%20may%20have%20regarding%20your%20condition.%20Please%20consult%20your%20doctor%20for%20the%20complete%20list%20of%20vaccine-preventable%20diseases%20and%20the%20complete%20vaccination%20schedule%20for%20each%20disease.%20The%20views%20and%20opinions%20of%20the%20Health%20Care%20Professional%20in%20this%20material%20are%20their%20own%20and%20does%20not%20reflect%20those%20of%20GSK.%C2%A0%20All%20scientific%20information%20is%20validated%2C%20for%20details%20write%20to%20us%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Aaskus%40gsk.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Easkus%40gsk.com%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ECL%20Code%3A%20NP-IN-HZU-ADVR-240002%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Col%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESimon%20AK%20et%20al.%20Proc%20Biol%20Sci%202015%3B282%3A2014%E2%80%933085.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EHarpaz%20R%20et%20al.%20MMWR%20Recomm%20Rep.%202008%20Jun%206%3B57(RR-5)%3A1-30.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EWeaver%20BA.%20J%20Am%20Osteopath%20Assoc.%202009%3B109(6%20Suppl%202)%3AS2%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3ECDC%20Shingles%20(Herpes%20Zoster)%20Clinical%20overview.%20Available%20from%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fshingles%2Fhcp%2Fclinical-overview.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EClinical%20Overview%20of%20Herpes%20Zoster%20(Shingles)%20%7C%20CDC%3C%2Fa%3E%20Accessed%20August%202023.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cdc.gov%2Fshingles%2Fabout%2Fsymptoms.html%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2